---

<BaseLayout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>RICS Home Surveys in Saltney | LEM Building Surveying</title>
    <meta content="Independent building surveyor in Saltney providing RICS Home Surveys and damp reports. Clear, honest advice direct from a local AssocRICS surveyor." name="description">
    <link href="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/saltney" rel="canonical">
    <meta content="RICS Home Surveys in Saltney | LEM Building Surveying" property="og:title">
    <meta content="Independent building surveyor in Saltney providing RICS Home Surveys and damp reports. Clear, honest advice direct from a local AssocRICS surveyor." property="og:description">
    <meta content="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/saltney" property="og:url">
    <meta content="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/logo-sticker.png" property="og:image">
    <meta content="summary_large_image" name="twitter:card">
    <meta content="RICS Home Surveys in Saltney | LEM Building Surveying" name="twitter:title">
    <meta content="Independent building surveyor in Saltney providing RICS Home Surveys and damp reports. Clear, honest advice direct from a local AssocRICS surveyor." name="twitter:description">
    <meta content="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/saltney" name="twitter:url">
    <meta content="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/logo-sticker.png" name="twitter:image">

    <!-- LocalBusiness Schema for Saltney -->
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "LocalBusiness",
        "name": "LEM Building Surveying Ltd",
        "url": "https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/saltney",
        "telephone": "+447378732037",
        "address": {
          "@type": "PostalAddress",
          "addressLocality": "Saltney",
          "addressRegion": "Flintshire",
          "postalCode": "CH4",
          "addressCountry": "GB"
        },
        "areaServed": "Saltney, Chester, Bretton, Lache, Broughton",
        "description": "Building surveyor for Saltney and surrounding areas offering RICS Home Surveys and property inspection services.",
        "image": "https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/logo-sticker.png"
      }
      </script>
      <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
        {
          "@context": "https://schema.org",
          "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
          "itemListElement": [
            {
              "@type": "ListItem",
              "position": 1,
              "name": "Home",
              "item": "https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/"
            },
            {
              "@type": "ListItem",
              "position": 2,
              "name": "Areas We Cover",
              "item": "https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/local-surveys"
            },
            {
              "@type": "ListItem",
              "position": 3,
              "name": "Saltney",
              "item": "https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/saltney"
            }
          ]
        }
      </script>
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Shared Header --><!-- HERO SECTION --><section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-container">
  <h1>RICS Home Surveys in Saltney</h1>
  <p>Buying, selling, or maintaining a property in Saltney? Get clear, local advice from a qualified independent surveyor.</p>
  <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry">Request a Quote</a>
  </div>
  </section><!-- MAIN CONTENT --><section class="service-detail">
  <div class="box-container">
  <h2>Your Independent Saltney Surveyor</h2>
  <p>
          LEM Building Surveying Ltd offers independent property inspections throughout Saltney, Bretton and the Chester fringe. Whether you're buying an older home or reviewing a modern property, you’ll receive straightforward advice and reports written by a local expert.
        </p>
  <h2>RICS Survey Services</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>Level 1 — Condition Report:</strong> Suitable for newer or well-maintained properties. Covers general condition using a traffic light system.</li>
  <li><strong>Level 2 — HomeBuyer Report:</strong> A mid-range survey ideal for most conventional properties. Includes repair advice and recommendations.</li>
  <li><strong>Level 3 — Building Survey:</strong> A detailed inspection and report for older or extended homes — includes structure, materials, defects and repair guidance.</li>
  <li><strong>Damp &amp; Timber Surveys:</strong> Pinpoint damp, mould or rot issues with expert diagnosis and next steps.</li>
  <li><strong>EPCs with Floorplans:</strong> Energy assessments with internal layout plans — perfect for sales or lettings.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Why Choose LEM?</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>Local to Saltney:</strong> Based just minutes away in Connah’s Quay, Liam knows the housing stock in Saltney well.</li>
  <li><strong>AssocRICS qualified:</strong> Professionally accredited and independent — not a corporate panel or national chain.</li>
  <li><strong>Clear, honest reporting:</strong> No jargon, no padding — just facts, risks and guidance.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Get Advice or Book Now</h2>
  <p>
          Still unsure which survey level you need? <a href="/comparison">Compare Level 1, 2 and 3 surveys</a> or <a href="/contact">ask Liam directly</a> for tailored advice.
        </p>
  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="cta-section">
  <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry">Get a Quote</a>
  <a class="secondary-button" href="/services">View All Services</a>
  </div>
  </div>
  <RelatedAreas currentSlug={currentSlug} />
  </section><!-- Shared Footer --><!-- Header & Footer Injection -->
</BaseLayout>
